            "body": "Same problem as #38648.\n\nWorkaround 1: set environment variable `NVIM_TEST=1`. Not guaranteed to keep working in the future.\nWorkaround 2: run the command in an terminal buffer.\nWorkaround 3: add a `:redraw` before calling `timer_start()`.",
